{"title":"从运河区滚出去","authors":["卡洛斯·张玛琳"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":1,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"从运河区滚出去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔巴拿马〕卡洛斯·张玛琳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在最后的战斗中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自豪的人民发出怒吼："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄发的美国佬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从运河区滚出去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国佬带来了他们的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大炮、美元和陆战队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在深重的苦难中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国失去了运河的土地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从巴拿马城到科伦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海盗的黑旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死亡的旗帜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"插向地峡的深处。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义的魔鬼们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从运河区滚出去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"除掉摇摆舞之外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还给我们带来无数的邪恶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们狂饮着威士忌酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而让我们替他们流血汗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄发的美国佬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想来征服我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了挽救"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正堕向深渊的祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们不惜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流尽我们的鲜血。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了镇压我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海军陆战队"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在街头路边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"散播着死亡的种子。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在卑污的旗帜下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成群的铁骑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无数的兽兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侵入了平原和山区。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自豪的人民发出怒吼："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从国境内滚出去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全世界人民正在觉醒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在巴拿马的土地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英勇的人民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举起斗争的大旗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们一秒钟也不能再容忍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那殖民主义的桎梏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在最后的战斗中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"觉醒的人民发出怒吼："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国佬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还我运河！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔孟复译〕〔原载《世界文学》〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}